nd appropriate behavior? These aren't questions you can answer with A/B tes=
ts or engagement metrics.</p><p style=3D"margin: 0 0 20px 0;color: rgb(54,5=
5,55);line-height: 26px;font-size: 16px;">There's also the problem of dispa=
rate impact. An AI system might have low overall rates of harmful output wh=
ile still causing significant harm to specific groups. Average metrics can =
